{"id":402618,"date":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":22}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"174","ytitle":"","mtitle":"竞赛","ftitle":"","authors":["冯昶祥"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海机床厂工人　冯昶祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看那个小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊腰虎背钢铁手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸红光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"操驾着那飞转的车头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对着他的是一台龙门铣床，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘立在龙头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手一挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切屑象缤纷的礼花飞向四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗在车床上飘扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子越千越有劲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奖状在龙门铣床上笑呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘越战越神气!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂台搭在他们中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子写着:要夺取她的奖状!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘写着:要夺取他的红旗!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他俩的生产指标哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始终并肩疾飞!"}]}